if not data_path.exists():

2. Trc quan ha vi Matplotlib

Case 1: Phn b kt qu bnh tiu ng

In[4]:
plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))
outcome_counts = diabetes_data['Outcome'].value_counts()
plt.bar(['Khng mc bnh (0)', 'Mc bnh (1)'], outcome_counts.values, 
        color=['lightblue', 'salmon'], alpha=0.7)
plt.xlabel('Kt qu')
plt.ylabel('S lng')
plt.title('Phn b kt qu bnh tiu ng')
for i, v in enumerate(outcome_counts.values):
    plt.text(i, v + 10, str(v), ha='center', va='bottom')
plt.grid(axis='y', alpha=0.3)
plt.show()

Nhn xt:

D liu khng cn bng vi khong 500 trng hp khng mc bnh v 268 trng hp mc bnh.

Case 2: So snh Glucose theo kt qu bnh

In[5]:
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))

# Tch d liu theo outcome
glucose_0 = diabetes_data[diabetes_data['Outcome'] == 0]['Glucose']
glucose_1 = diabetes_data[diabetes_data['Outcome'] == 1]['Glucose']

plt.hist(glucose_0, bins=20, alpha=0.7, label='Khng mc bnh', color='lightblue')
plt.hist(glucose_1, bins=20, alpha=0.7, label='Mc bnh', color='salmon')

plt.xlabel('Nng  Glucose')
plt.ylabel('Tn sut')
plt.title('Phn b Glucose theo kt qu bnh tiu ng')
plt.legend()
plt.grid(alpha=0.3)
plt.show()

Nhn xt:

Ngi mc bnh tiu ng c xu hng c nng glucose cao hn.

Case 3: Mi quan h gia Tui v BMI

In[6]:
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
colors = ['lightblue', 'salmon']
outcomes = [0, 1]
labels = ['Khng mc bnh', 'Mc bnh']

for i, outcome in enumerate(outcomes):
    subset = diabetes_data[diabetes_data['Outcome'] == outcome]
    plt.scatter(subset['Age'], subset['BMI'], 
               alpha=0.6, c=colors[i], label=labels[i])

plt.xlabel('Tui')
plt.ylabel('Ch s BMI')
plt.title('Mi quan h gia Tui v BMI theo kt qu bnh')
plt.legend()
plt.grid(alpha=0.3)
plt.show()

Nhn xt:

Khng c mi quan h r rng gia tui v BMI vi kt qu bnh.

3. Trc quan ha vi Seaborn

Case 1: Boxplot so snh cc ch s theo kt qu bnh

In[7]:
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
features = ['Glucose', 'BMI', 'Age', 'Insulin']
fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(15, 10))

for i, feature in enumerate(features):
    row, col = i // 2, i % 2
    sns.boxplot(data=diabetes_data, x='Outcome', y=feature, ax=axes[row, col], 
               palette=['lightblue', 'salmon'])
    axes[row, col].set_title(f'Phn b {feature} theo Outcome')
    axes[row, col].set_xticklabels(['Khng mc', 'Mc bnh'])

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

Case 2: Heatmap tng quan

In[8]:
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))
correlation_matrix = diabetes_data.corr()
mask = np.triu(np.ones_like(correlation_matrix, dtype=bool))

sns.heatmap(correlation_matrix, mask=mask, annot=True, cmap='coolwarm', 
            center=0, square=True, linewidths=0.5)
plt.title('Ma trn tng quan gia cc bin')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

Nhn xt:

  • Glucose c tng quan dng mnh nht vi Outcome (0.47)
  • Age v Pregnancies c tng quan vi nhau (0.54)
  • Cc bin khc c tng quan yu vi Outcome

Case 3: Pairplot cho cc bin quan trng

In[9]:
important_features = ['Glucose', 'BMI', 'Age', 'DiabetesPedigreeFunction', 'Outcome']
sns.pairplot(diabetes_data[important_features], hue='Outcome', 
             palette=['lightblue', 'salmon'], diag_kind='kde')
plt.suptitle('Pairplot ca cc bin quan trng', y=1.02)
plt.show()

Nhn xt:

ng cho (Distribution plots):

  • Glucose: Phn phi ca ngi mc bnh lch phi r rt, cho thy glucose cao l du hiu quan trng
  • BMI: Ngi mc bnh c phn phi BMI nhnh hn, tp trung khong 30-35
  • Age: Ngi ln tui (trn 30) c t l mc bnh cao hn
  • DiabetesPedigreeFunction: Phn phi ca ngi mc bnh c ui di hn, ch s di truyn cao hn

Cc scatter plot quan trng:

  • Glucose vs BMI: Mi quan h tuyn tnh yu, nhng ngi mc bnh tp trung gc trn bn phi (glucose cao + BMI cao)
  • Glucose vs Age: Ngi tr c glucose cao vn c nguy c mc bnh
  • DiabetesPedigreeFunction vs Glucose: Tng quan kh r - ch s di truyn cao kt hp glucose cao lm tng nguy c

4. Phn tch su hn

Phn b theo s ln mang thai

In[10]:
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
pregnancy_outcome = diabetes_data.groupby(['Pregnancies', 'Outcome']).size().unstack()
pregnancy_outcome.plot(kind='bar', stacked=True, color=['lightblue', 'salmon'])
plt.xlabel('S ln mang thai')
plt.ylabel('S lng')
plt.title('Phn b kt qu theo s ln mang thai')
plt.legend(['Khng mc bnh', 'Mc bnh'])
plt.xticks(rotation=45)
plt.grid(axis='y', alpha=0.3)
plt.show()

<Figure size 1200x600 with 0 Axes>

Nhn xt:

Xu hng theo s ln mang thai:

  • 0 ln mang thai: T l mc bnh thp (~25%), ch yu l nam gii hoc ph n cha sinh con
  • 1-5 ln mang thai: T l mc bnh tng dn, t ~30% ln ~45%
  • 6-10 ln mang thai: T l mc bnh cao (~50-60%), c bit nhm 9-10 ln
  • Trn 10 ln: T l mc bnh rt cao (>65%)

Hin tng ng ch :

  • Tiu ng thai k: S ln mang thai nhiu lm tng nguy c tiu ng type 2 sau ny
  • tui: S ln mang thai nhiu thng i km vi tui cao
  • Hormonal changes: Nhng thay i hormone trong thai k nh hng n khng insulin

Phn tch theo nhm tui

In[11]:
# To nhm tui
diabetes_data['AgeGroup'] = pd.cut(diabetes_data['Age'], 
                                 bins=[20, 30, 40, 50, 60, 100], 
                                 labels=['20-30', '30-40', '40-50', '50-60', '60+'])

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
age_outcome = diabetes_data.groupby(['AgeGroup', 'Outcome']).size().unstack()
age_outcome.plot(kind='bar', stacked=True, color=['lightblue', 'salmon'])
plt.xlabel('Nhm tui')
plt.ylabel('S lng')
plt.title('Phn b kt qu theo nhm tui')
plt.legend(['Khng mc bnh', 'Mc bnh'])
plt.grid(axis='y', alpha=0.3)
plt.show()
